## GitHub metadata sync

Source of truth: [.github/repo-description.txt](../../.github/repo-description.txt).

```bash
make sync-github-metadata   # requires gh CLI; edits repo description on GitHub
```

On push to `main`, [`.github/workflows/docs.yml`](../../.github/workflows/docs.yml) syncs when `repo-description.txt` changes.
